ids_alerts.rule_msg: SERVER-OTHER Squid HTTP Vary response header denial of service attempt
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"SERVER-OTHER Squid HTTP Vary response header denial of service attempt"; flow:to_client,established; http_header; content:"Vary|3A|"; content:!"|0D 0A|",within 250; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:http; reference:cve,2016-2569; reference:url,www.squid-cache.org/Advisories/SQUID-2016_2.txt; classtype:denial-of-service; sid:41379; rev:1; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: INDICATOR-OBFUSCATION potential javascript unescape obfuscation attempt detected

ids_alerts.rule_msg: SERVER-OTHER Beetel Connection Manager username buffer overflow attempt

ids_alerts.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $FILE_DATA_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute"; flow:to_client,established; file_data; content:"<script"; content:"src=",within 30; isdataat:100,relative; content:!"|2E|js",within 100; service:ftp-data,http,imap,pop3; reference:cve,2014-6345; reference:url,technet.microsoft.com/en-us/security/bulletin/MS14-065; classtype:policy-violation; sid:32481; rev:3; )
